values:
The goddess of Harmony. You can get along with
pretty much anyone. You are able to fit into
any type of crowd and can be popular one day,
or not noticed the next. You keep ALL your
friends in check by stating obvious solutions
and telling them to never regret anything they
do in life. Because of your logic, people DO
sometimes find it hard to get along with you,
but once you assure them that your logic only
comes when is needed, they open up to you and
can tell you anything. You are most likely the
"shoulder-to-cry-on" in your group(s)
of friends and many people look up to you! Your
power would be to unite all universes with your
logic.

What are you a Goddess of? - (with anime pics)
brought to you by Quizilla If you'd like to see more of me, I'm at Myspace too:

Check me out!

cuddle and a kiss on the forehead - you like to be
close to your special someone and feel warm,
comfortable, and needed

He is a Man
You have yourself a perfect gentleman and a total keeper Your guy almost always acts appropriately He's probably even very upstanding when you're not around There's no boy left in your boyfriend - he's all man!
Is He A Boy or a Man?

You Are a Passionate Kisser
You are the most likely type to kiss a sexy stranger

Your kissing style is unpredictable and free spirited

You could kiss anyone at a drop of a hat

It's all about where your passion leads you
What's Your Kissing Style?

I am just joining after a few years of all my friends being hyped about this live journal stuff. I thought it was just another way for everyone to know everything about everyone else and therefore it would just be more drama in my life. But then I realized that it would be so much easier to communicate with my friends cause when schedules conflict we can know whats on each others' minds. My life now consists of strictly boyfriend drama and thats no fun. I'm happy everyone bugged me to play around with this stuff. 
             Love, Adrie :p
